LoopINLoopOUT
-------------------------------------------
Sample, Loop, and Stem repository. The application is all about remixing, creating and sharing. 
The audio player will be similar to sound cloud, as a really like to build on that idea, and the commenting
is very ideal for commenting on audio.
 

- Dependencies: 
https://github.com/benalavi/waveform
This gem is used to generate waveform from wav to png
	- Depends on ruby-audio gem
	- Depends on oily_png
	- Depends on chunky_png
On OSX or linux you need to have: 
mac: brew install libsndfile
	 brew install ffmpeg

linux - apt-get install libsndfile1-dev
